ail. It also creates<strong> two </strong>additional thumbnails that you can switch to, in case you don&#8217;t like the default one.</p>\n<p>You can test this on our <a href=\"http://test.com/bpm-ffmpeg/\">live demo server</a>. Also following screenshot shows interface to select thumbnail:</p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-26651\" alt=\"buddypress-media-ffmpeg-video-thumbail-selection\" src=\"http://cdn.rtcamp.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/buddypress-media-ffmpeg-video-thumbail-selection.png\" width=\"568\" height=\"475\" /></p>\n<h3><img style=\' float: right; padding: 4px; margin: 0 0 2px 7px;\'  class=\"alignright size-full wp-image-26656\" alt=\"spanish-translation\" src=\"http://cdn.rtcamp.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/spanish-translation-e1360928385420.png\" width=\"240\" height=\"191\" />SpanishÂ Translation Added</h3>\n<p>A while ago,Â <a title=\"BuddyPress Media 2.5 is friendlier. It also speaks more languages\" href=\"http://rtcamp.com/news/buddypress-media-2-5-is-friendlier-it-also-speaks-more-languages/\" target=\"_blank\">BuddyPress Media got translation ready</a>Â and now ships withÂ <a title=\"rtCamp BuddyPress Media Translation Project\" href=\"http://rtcamp.com/translate/projects/buddypress-media\" target=\"_blank\">multiple languages</a>.</p>\n<p>Now, BuddyPress Media FFMPEG Converter is translation ready, as well. In fact, this version includes theÂ <a title=\"BuddyPress Media FFMPEG Converter Spanish Translation\" href=\"http://rtcamp.com/translate/projects/buddypress-media-ffmpeg/es/default\" target=\"_blank\">Spanish translation</a>.</p>\n<p>You can addÂ your ownÂ translations on ourÂ <a title=\"BuddyPress Media FFMPEG Converter Translation Project\" href=\"http://rtcamp.com/translate/projects/buddypress-media-ffmpeg\" target=\"_blank\">translation project</a>Â or directly to your copy.</p>\n<h3>Media-node updated</h3>\n<p>To support video-thumbnail generation, we need to updateÂ <a title=\"Media Node\" href=\"http://rtcamp.com/media-node/\" target=\"_blank\">Media node</a>Â project also.</p>\n<p>Please upgrade your media-node setup, before you upgrade toÂ BuddyPress-Media FFMPEG Converter v1.4. Depending on how you have installed media-node, upgrade process will only requireÂ <code>git pull</code><span style=\"line-height: 14px;\">Â andÂ </span>restarting media-node.</p>\n<p>If you have used ourÂ installationÂ script, then you can simply log-in to your terminal and run following command:</p>\n<pre><code class=\"bash\">curl https://raw.github.com/rtCamp/media-node/master/setup/update.sh | sudo bash</code></pre>\n<p>If you face any issue, please use our <a href=\"http://rtcamp.com/support/forum/buddypress-media/\">support forum</a>.</p>\n<h3>Automatic update forÂ BuddyPress-Media FFMPEG Converter</h3>\n<p>If you are usingÂ BuddyPress-Media FFMPEG Converter v1.3 then you will see automatic update notice as you see for standard WordPress plugins hosted on wordpress.org repo. Just click &#8220;Update&#8221; button to upgradeÂ BuddyPress-Media FFMPEG Converter to v1.4.</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://cdn.rtcamp.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/update.png\"><img class=\"size-large wp-image-26487 alignnone\" alt=\"update\" src=\"http://cdn.rtcamp.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/update-560x350.png\" width=\"560\" height=\"350\" /></a></p>\n<p>For customers runningÂ BuddyPress-Media FFMPEG Converter v1.2, please download v1.4 from your <a href=\"https://rtcamp.com/my-account/\">account center</a>.</p>\n<p>All customers willÂ receiveÂ future updates automatically.</p>\n<p>If you haven&#8217;t purchaseÂ BuddyPress-Media FFMPEG yet, its time to buy it.</p>\n<p>We are working on some major features for future release. Once they are ready, there will be price hike. Old customers will always get price-hike protection. <img src=\'http://cdn.rtcamp.com/wp-includes/images/smilies/icon_smile.gif\' alt=\':-)\' class=\'wp-smiley\' /> </p>\n<p><strong>Link: </strong><a href=\"https://rtcamp.com/my-account/\">Download 