er foreign language, which you are well-versed with.</p>\n<p>Steps to translate BuddyPress Media into the language of your choice are covered in previous <a href=\"https://rtcamp.com/tutorials/buddypress-media-translation/\">post here</a>.</p>\n<h4>What&#8217;s New in 2.4?</h4>\n<p>The new BuddyPress Media 2.4 is fast, readable and lightweight. This 2.4 version will remain as a strong foundation for future feature-packed releases. BuddyPress 2.4 also offers:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Enhanced User Interface</li>\n<li>Removed dependency on jQuery UI (commonly requested change)</li>\n<li>Well structured codes</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Why Refactor?</h4>\n<p>Refactoring simplyÂ improvesÂ the code readability. Refactoring of BuddyPress Media has helped us reduce code complexity andÂ dependancies. The new BuddyPress Media 2.4 is well structured and lightweight, which improves the overall user experience.</p>\n<h4>What&#8217;s Next?</h4>\n<p>As mentioned above, BuddyPress Media 2.4 is a strong foundation for some feature packed update (coming soon). Editing album names, better mediaÂ organisationÂ and sorting, improved support for iOS uploads &amp; revamped upload functionality are few of the expected features on-route to 2.5.</p>\n<p>More details about our future plans can be found inÂ <a href=\"http://rtcamp.com/buddypress-media/roadmap/\">our roadmap page</a>.</p>\n<p>Thanks Saurabh Shukla, Joshua Abenazer, Faishal Saiyed and Hrishikesh VaipurkarÂ for all theÂ hard-work.</p>\n<p><strong>Links:</strong>Â <a href=\"http://wordpress.org/extend/plugins/buddypress-media/\">Download BuddyPress Media 2.4</a>Â |Â <a href=\"http://test.com/buddypress-media\">Live Demo</a>Â |Â <a href=\"http://rtcamp.com/store/buddypress-media-ffmpeg/\">PremiumÂ Addons</a></p>\n<div class=\'yarpp-related-rss\'>\n<p>Related Posts:<ol>\n<li><a href=\'http://rtcamp.com/news/buddypress-media-2-3-released-with-group-media/\' rel=\'bookmark\' title=\'BuddyPress Media 2.3 released with Group-Media\'>BuddyPress Media 2.3 released with Group-Media</a></li>\n<li><a href=\'http://rtcamp.com/news/media-activity-streaming-added-to-buddypress-media-component/\' rel=\'bookmark\' title=\'Media Activity Streaming added to Buddypress Media Component\'>Media Activity Streaming added to Buddypress Media Component</a></li>\n<li><a href=\'http://rtcamp.com/news/buddypress-media-2-2-released-with-user-albums-and-more/\' rel=\'bookmark\' title=\'BuddyPress Media 2.2 Released with User Albums and more\'>BuddyPress Media 2.2 Released with User Albums and more</a></li>\n</ol></p>\n</div>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:60:\"http://rtcamp.com/news/buddypress-media-2-4-refactored/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:5;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:48:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:46:\"BuddyPress Media 2.3 released with Group-Media\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:70:\"http://rtcamp.com/news/buddypress-media-2-3-released-with-group-media/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:79:\"http://rtcamp.com/news/buddypress-media-2-3-released-with-group-media/#comments\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s