8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:131:\"It has been 3 months since we launched updated version of BuddyPress Media. And now, today we\'ve crossed 10000 downloads milestone.\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:13:\"Shahzad Saeed\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:3586:\"<p>It has been 3 months since we launched updated version of <a title=\"BuddyPress Media\" href=\"http://rtcamp.com/buddypress-media/\">BuddyPress Media</a>. And now, today we&#8217;ve crossed <a title=\"10000+ downloads\" href=\"http://wordpress.org/extend/plugins/buddypress-media/stats/\">10000+ downloads</a> milestone.</p>\n<p>It really make us proud to say that thousands of webmasters around the world have adopted BuddyPress Media so far to power their BuddyPress site with multimedia sharing capabilities. We&#8217;ve also launched <a title=\"BuddyPress Media FFMPEG\" href=\"http://rtcamp.com/store/buddypress-media-ffmpeg-converter/\">add-on</a> <a title=\"BuddyPress Media Kaltura\" href=\"http://rtcamp.com/store/buddypress-media-kaltura/\">plugins</a> to add automatic audio/video conversion support.</p>\n<p><img style=\' display: block; margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto;\'  class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-21927\" title=\"BuddyPress Media 10000 Downloads\" src=\"http://cdn.rtcamp.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/11/10000.jpg\" alt=\"BuddyPress Media 10000 Downloads\" width=\"450\" height=\"283\" /></p>\n<p>For last 3 days we&#8217;ve seen 300+ downloads per day. If things keep going like this, 20000+ milestones can be crossed within next 30 days. <img src=\'http://cdn.rtcamp.com/wp-includes/images/smilies/icon_wink.gif\' alt=\';)\' class=\'wp-smiley\' /> </p>\n<p><img style=\' display: block; margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto;\'  class=\"aligncenter rtp-img-shadow size-full wp-image-21946\" title=\"downloads.png\" src=\"http://cdn.rtcamp.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/11/downloads.png\" alt=\"download stat\" width=\"454\" height=\"480\" /></p>\n<p>We&#8217;ve been receiving valuable feedback and feature requests from our users. Our team is striving hard to implement <a title=\"BuddyPress Media Roadmap\" href=\"http://rtcamp.com/buddypress-media/roadmap/\">more new features</a> as per the feedback to make BuddyPress Media more powerful plugin. Feel free to track our progress, request a feature or report an issue on <a title=\"GitHub\" href=\"https://github.com/rtCamp/buddypress-media/\">github</a>.</p>\n<p>In next release (v 2.3), we will be adding group-album support and more.</p>\n<p>Thank you all for your continued support <img src=\'http://cdn.rtcamp.com/wp-includes/images/smilies/icon_smile.gif\' alt=\':)\' class=\'wp-smiley\' /> </p>\n<p><strong>Links:</strong> <a title=\"Download BuddyPress Media\" href=\"http://wordpress.org/extend/plugins/buddypress-media/\">Download BuddyPress Media</a> | <a title=\"Live Demo\" href=\"http://test.com/buddypress-media\">Live Demo</a> | <a title=\"Fork us on GitHub\" href=\"https://github.com/rtCamp/buddypress-media/\">Fork us on GitHub</a> | <a title=\"BuddyPress Media FFMPEG\" href=\"http://rtcamp.com/store/buddypress-media-ffmpeg/\">Premium</a> <a title=\"BuddyPress Media Kaltura\" href=\"http://rtcamp.com/store/buddypress-media-kaltura/\">Addons</a></p>\n<div class=\'yarpp-related-rss\'>\n<p>Related Posts:<ol>\n<li><a href=\'http://rtcamp.com/news/buddypress-media-2-3-released-with-group-media/\' rel=\'bookmark\' title=\'BuddyPress Media 2.3 released with Group-Media\'>BuddyPress Media 2.3 released with Group-Media</a></li>\n<li><a href=\'http://rtcamp.com/news/buddypress-medi