ddypress-media-kaltura/\">BuddyPress Media Kaltura</a>.Â This addon supports Kaltura.com and self-hosted Kaltura-CE setup.</p>\n<p>As this is an add-on for open-source <a href=\"http://wordpress.org/extend/plugins/buddypress-media/\">BuddyPress Media plugin</a>, BuddyPress community members will be able to upload photos &amp;Â videosÂ using their mobile devices (including iPhone/iPad running iOS6).</p>\n<p>You can use this addon, if you want to start a facebook or youtube like community where uses can upload videos in popular video-formats like AVI, MPEG.</p>\n<p>We will be preparing a live demo shortly.</p>\n<h3>How it works!</h3>\n<p>Following will help you visualize everything together.</p>\n<p><img class=\"size-full wp-image-15205 alignnone\" title=\"BuddyPress Media Kaltura\" src=\"http://cdn.rtcamp.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/BPM1.png\" alt=\"BuddyPress Media Kaltura\" width=\"607\" height=\"314\" /></p>\n<p>If you still have any questions, feel free to ask us in comments below orÂ you can use ourÂ <a href=\"http://rtcamp.com/support\">free support forum</a>.</p>\n<p><strong>Links:</strong>Â <a href=\"http://rtcamp.com/store/buddypress-media-kaltura/\">BuddyPress-Media Kaltura Addon</a>Â | Demo</p>\n<div class=\'yarpp-related-rss\'>\n<p>Related Posts:<ol>\n<li><a href=\'http://rtcamp.com/news/buddypress-media-2-1-released-with-add-on-support/\' rel=\'bookmark\' title=\'BuddyPress Media 2.1 released with Add-on Support\'>BuddyPress Media 2.1 released with Add-on Support</a></li>\n<li><a href=\'http://rtcamp.com/news/buddypress-media-kaltura-addon-released/\' rel=\'bookmark\' title=\'BuddyPress Media Kaltura Addon Released\'>BuddyPress Media Kaltura Addon Released</a></li>\n<li><a href=\'http://rtcamp.com/news/buddypress-media-2-2-released-with-user-albums-and-more/\' rel=\'bookmark\' title=\'BuddyPress Media 2.2 Released with User Albums and more\'>BuddyPress Media 2.2 Released with User Albums and more</a></li>\n</ol></p>\n</div>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s